snippet.title: Zelda Mystery of Solarus DX trailer 2
snippet.description:
Zelda: Mystery of Solarus DX is a free, open-source 2D Zelda fangame. It is set to be a direct sequel to Zelda: A Link to the Past on the SNES, using the same graphics and game mechanisms. Available on https://www.solarus-games.org/en/games/the-legend-of-zelda-mystery-of-solarus-dx

Zelda Mystery of Solarus DX est un Zelda amateur en 2D et open-source. Le jeu est basé sur les graphismes de A Link to the Past mais y ajoute certains graphismes inédits et des musiques originales. Disponible sur https://www.solarus-games.org/en/games/the-legend-of-zelda-mystery-of-solarus-dx.
